Description:

The Agriculture Department, Assam, Khanapara issued a total of 1837 for the posts of Agril. Extension Asstt (AEA), Jr Asstt, Stenographer, Steno-Typist, Electrician. The online application for the posts of Agril. Extension Asstt (AEA), Jr Asstt, Stenographer, Steno-Typist, Electrician under Agriculture Department, Assam, Khanapara shall start from 27-02-2021. The eligible candidates must submit the online application before 13-03-2021. Check the complete details below so that all the doubts about the filling of the online application get cleared. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The mode of application is online and after filling in the required details you have to provide the billing details for the application fee.

  • The examination fee is as per rules
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

The Starting date to apply for this online application form is 22-03-2021

The Last date to apply for this online application form is 12-04-2021

Age limit criteria:

To apply for this job you must have fallen in the age limit criteria provided by the Agriculture Department, Assam, Khanapara :

  • The minimum age limit to apply is:18 Years
  • The maximum age limit to apply is: 40 years
  • For age relaxation criteria you can refer to the notification given below in The ProGrad jobs.

How to apply for Agriculture Dept., Assam Various Vacancy Online Form 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Agriculture Department, Assam, Khanapara.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Agriculture Dept., Assam.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
